{"tid":758149,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"區樂軒：自己每日上班10多小時工時長","createTime":"2018-07-27T11:58:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-27T16:39:12.000Z","uid":73883,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5e26f14947ef74d57c0473bc7093ea9a71773a2b","tid":758149,"uid":73883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T11:58:21.000Z","msg":"在樓價高、物價貴、競爭激烈的香港社會，生兒育女似是一個遙不可及的願望。即使是年僅31歲、月薪逾9.6萬元的立法會議員區諾軒，也慨嘆工時太長，惟有與太太一起事業至上，把「生仔」退為「一個好次要嘅目標」。<br />\n<br />\n區稱，與太太每日上班10多小時，難有能力盡父母責任，倒不如着眼目前，努力工作及照顧家人」。他又認為，不少80後或90後覺得生兒育女已非人生必要目標，「因為呢個社會太多嘢風高浪急，倒不如盡量爭取先」。"},{"pid":"e9e430cabc41384a2fb378ee86130c780ef91ec8","tid":758149,"uid":73883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T11:59:02.000Z","msg":"原來咁撚辛苦，唔怪得唔開會都要去日本 hea 下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56c239787854790872c2c8bef9689719241dc721","tid":758149,"uid":24284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9e430cabc41384a2fb378ee86130c780ef91ec8","tid":758149,"uid":73883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T11:59:02.000Z","msg":"原來咁撚辛苦，唔怪得唔開會都要去日本 hea 下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T12:10:49.000Z","msg":"訂好晒機票嘛，人地堂堂尊貴議員，緊係唔可以攰親<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25ec9591829772d2f8ad0c6c50e5a18b06cddc3a","tid":758149,"uid":58852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T16:39:12.000Z","msg":"10多小時個range 好大<br />\n11-19hr per day<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}